  "keyFeatures": [
    "Search and explore 50,000+ datasets from data.gouv.fr",
    "Query tabular data directly via Tabular API",
    "Download and parse large CSV, JSON, and JSONL files",
    "Access external dataservices (APIs) with OpenAPI specs",
    "Get usage metrics (visits, downloads) for datasets and resources",
    "Connect with 15+ AI chatbots (Claude, ChatGPT, Gemini, etc.)",
    "Streamable HTTP transport with health monitoring",
    "Docker-ready deployment with environment configuration",
    "Comprehensive error handling and logging",
    "Production-ready with Sentry monitoring"
